wool table
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a table in a woolshed upon which fleeces are spread, trimmed and rolled.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: wool-table, wooltable
